1
00:00:11,790 --> 00:00:13,030
Five hundred years ago,

2
00:00:13,050 --> 00:00:15,810
the war between gods and demons shattered the celestial ladder.

3
00:00:16,550 --> 00:00:17,910
The left hand of Deity Taihe,

4
00:00:17,910 --> 00:00:19,670
which concentrated the power of all gods,

5
00:00:19,790 --> 00:00:21,270
fell into the mortal world.

6
00:00:21,950 --> 00:00:24,150
Having lost his primordial divine power,

7
00:00:24,160 --> 00:00:26,930
he was lost in the void, unable to awaken.

8
00:00:27,190 --> 00:00:29,180
The Divine Realm weakened as a result.

9
00:00:29,390 --> 00:00:31,990
Gods fell one after another,

10
00:00:32,820 --> 00:00:35,550
and the mortal world was cut off from the Divine Realm.

11
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:37,060
Only the human race

12
00:00:37,090 --> 00:00:40,490
and two immortal clans, the Youhu Clan and the War Demons,

13
00:00:40,800 --> 00:00:42,880
stayed in the mortal world.

14
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:17,770
[A Moment But Forever]

15
00:02:18,940 --> 00:02:20,670
[Episode 1]

16
00:02:21,990 --> 00:02:23,220
My name is Ji Tanyin.

17
00:02:23,630 --> 00:02:25,870
People also call me Goddess Wushuang.

18
00:02:26,870 --> 00:02:28,150
A thousand years ago, I ascended to the Divine Realm

19
00:02:28,150 --> 00:02:29,300
through my craftsmanship.

20
00:02:29,460 --> 00:02:31,100
As the creator of the divine hand,

21
00:02:31,310 --> 00:02:33,310
I went to the mortal world to search for it.

22
00:02:33,700 --> 00:02:35,230
However, with the celestial ladder shattered

23
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:36,780
and the passage between realms destroyed,

24
00:02:37,190 --> 00:02:38,900
I was severely injured as I passed through

25
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:40,030
the Sea of Flux.

26
00:02:40,430 --> 00:02:41,950
After a near-death experience,

27
00:02:42,079 --> 00:02:43,400
I was trapped on Wu Mountain.

28
00:02:45,090 --> 00:02:46,050
After I woke up,

29
00:02:46,430 --> 00:02:47,630
I learned that the Youhu Clan

30
00:02:47,660 --> 00:02:49,829
had produced a prodigious young man.

31
00:02:49,850 --> 00:02:50,650
I suspected

32
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:52,579
that the Divine Hand might be in his possession.

33
00:02:52,610 --> 00:02:54,329
So I rushed to the Pinghu battlefield.

34
00:03:11,870 --> 00:03:12,870
That young man was indeed

35
00:03:12,870 --> 00:03:14,350
the new host of the Divine Hand.

36
00:03:14,470 --> 00:03:15,630
However, he couldn't

37
00:03:15,630 --> 00:03:17,380
fully control the power of the Divine Hand yet.

38
00:03:19,430 --> 00:03:20,190
Stop!

39
00:03:27,100 --> 00:03:28,100
With a single strike,

40
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:30,590
he nearly shattered the entire Pinghu.

41
00:03:30,790 --> 00:03:31,670
To save lives,

42
00:03:31,690 --> 00:03:32,940
I intercepted half of his attack,

43
00:03:32,970 --> 00:03:34,480
sustaining severe injuries myself.

44
00:03:34,590 --> 00:03:35,790
Along with half of Pinghu,

45
00:03:35,790 --> 00:03:37,150
I sank into the sea.

46
00:03:40,310 --> 00:03:40,950
Tanyin.

47
00:03:42,210 --> 00:03:42,850
Tanyin.

48
00:03:43,470 --> 00:03:44,750
You must go to Fangwai Mountain

49
00:03:44,780 --> 00:03:46,190
to retrieve the Divine Left Hand.

50
00:03:46,590 --> 00:03:47,950
The High Priest of Youhu Clan

51
00:03:47,950 --> 00:03:49,270
