136
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,150
You will soon meet

137
00:08:06,180 --> 00:08:08,020
your destined benefactor.

138
00:08:08,050 --> 00:08:09,170
She comes from an extraordinary background

139
00:08:09,170 --> 00:08:10,220
