142
00:08:12,810 --> 00:08:14,570
No more misfortunes will befall you.

143
00:08:18,260 --> 00:08:19,580
Good health.

144
00:08:19,580 --> 00:08:19,850
Yes.

145
00:08:19,850 --> 00:08:21,280
Everything goes smoothly.

146
00:08:21,410 --> 00:08:22,250
Indeed.

