149
00:08:28,820 --> 00:08:30,970
Trust me, it will surely be accurate.

150
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:34,320
Trust me, it will surely be accurate!

151
00:08:42,940 --> 00:08:44,169
Is the lantern heavy?

152
00:08:44,410 --> 00:08:45,690
Do you need help with it?

153
00:08:45,900 --> 00:08:46,690
No need.

154
00:08:53,700 --> 00:08:56,220
This is a divine lantern. It will extinguish if it touches the ground.

155
00:08:56,460 --> 00:08:57,240
If the light goes out,

156
00:08:57,290 --> 00:08:58,780
you won't be able to enter the mountain.

157
00:09:01,450 --> 00:09:03,010
It has a sinking stone on it.

158
00:09:32,900 --> 00:09:34,450
