159
00:09:34,810 --> 00:09:36,210
Just pick any one.

160
00:09:36,650 --> 00:09:37,970
Why hesitate here?

161
00:09:58,770 --> 00:10:00,530
Are you an immortal residing on this mountain?

162
00:10:00,850 --> 00:10:01,650
Yes.

163
00:10:02,650 --> 00:10:03,580
Then why don't you

164
00:10:03,580 --> 00:10:04,460
