168
00:10:10,130 --> 00:10:11,380
How can I guide you?

169
00:10:11,970 --> 00:10:13,090
I'm a human sent here

170
00:10:13,090 --> 00:10:14,140
as a maid candidate.

171
00:10:14,140 --> 00:10:15,220
I'm from Pingzhou,

172
00:10:15,220 --> 00:10:16,720
