00:27:04,170 --> 00:27:05,490
causing your qi and blood to churn.

560
00:27:05,690 --> 00:27:07,450
At worst, it will severely injure your spirit,

561
00:27:07,450 --> 00:27:08,770
destroying all your cultivation.

562
00:27:08,770 --> 00:27:10,360
You must remember this well.

563
00:27:11,210 --> 00:27:12,090
Don't worry.

564
00:27:12,120 --> 00:27:13,410
I have craftsmanship skills to rely on,

565
00:27:13,530 --> 00:27:14,760
and I know some martial arts techniques.

566
00:27:14,870 --> 00:27:16,490
I don't need to rely on divine power for everything.

567
00:27:16,880 --> 00:27:19,200
Besides, I created the Divine Hand.

568
00:27:19,200 --> 00:27:20,450
I know what to do.

569
00:27:21,600 --> 00:27:22,410
Oh, right.

570
00:27:22,480 --> 00:27:24,440
You mentioned earlier that you wanted to go to Fangwai Mountain

571
00:27:24,440 --> 00:27:25,530
to find a young man.

572
00:27:25,730 --> 00:27:27,320
He's one of your followers.

573
00:27:27,320 --> 00:27:28,440
Did you find him?

574
00:28:11,840 --> 00:28:13,320
When he saved me back then,

575
00:28:13,610 --> 00:28:15,080
he was still a spirit fox.

576
00:28:15,460 --> 00:28:17,800
That half of the jade token was also taken by him.

577
00:28:21,480 --> 00:28:22,170
Now,

578
00:28:22,630 --> 00:28:23,870
I don't know where he is.

579
00:28:29,570 --> 00:28:30,650
Time has passed,

580
00:28:30,850 --> 00:28:32,010
and he has already grown up.

581
00:28:32,160 --> 00:28:33,680
His appearance has also changed.

582
00:28:33,800 --> 00:28:35,760
It shouldn't be that easy to find him.

583
00:28:36,080 --> 00:28:37,810
You are the God of Craftsmanship,

584
00:28:37,810 --> 00:28:38,760
with countless followers.

585
00:28:38,760 --> 00:28:39,960
Why do you insist on finding

586
00:28:39,960 --> 00:28:40,960
this particular one?

587
00:28:41,770 --> 00:28:42,720
He's different.

588
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:45,360
But please rest assured, Mr. Loong,

589
00:28:46,290 --> 00:28:47,700
I won't neglect my duties for personal reasons.

590
00:28:54,480 --> 00:28:55,450
Madam Zhi Dai.

591
00:28:57,560 --> 00:28:59,000
You've been away from home for 40 years.

592
00:28:59,000 --> 00:28:59,810
Don't you miss

593
00:28:59,810 --> 00:29:01,080
your family?

594
00:29:01,330 --> 00:29:02,960
Your father is nearly 90 years old.

595
00:29:02,960 --> 00:29:04,480
Living to 70 has been rare since ancient times.

596
00:29:04,510 --> 00:29:07,150
Think about it, how much time does he have left?

597
00:29:10,610 --> 00:29:11,400
Young Mistress Dai,

598
00:29:11,760 --> 00:29:13,080
may I have a word with you in private?

599
00:29:15,970 --> 00:29:16,890
My father,

600
00:29:17,130 --> 00:29:18,180
how is he?

601
00:29:19,320 --> 00:29:20,680
The City Lord has grown old.

602
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:23,280
These past two years, he's been very ill.

603
00:29:23,570 --> 00:29:24,640
When I left,

604
00:29:25,040 --> 00:29:26,450
he was already bedridden.

605
00:29:27,090 --> 00:29:29,690
That's why I took the liberty

606
00:29:29,990 --> 00:29:31,190
to come see you without permission.

607
00:29:33,730 --> 00:29:35,810
But seeing you today,

608
00:29:37,160 --> 00:29:38,890
you're no different from those

609
00:29:38,890 --> 00:29:40,730
maids of our clan who are dogmatically controlled

610
00:29:41,080 --> 00:29:42,550
by the Youhu Clan.

611
00:29:44,040 --> 00:29:45,110
What are you trying to say?

612
00:29:48,650 --> 00:29:49,670
Pardon me.

613
00:29:49,710 --> 00:29:51,230
I humbly request you to descend the mountain

614
00:29:51,250 --> 00:29:52,370
and return to Yandu,

615
00:29:52,850 --> 00:29:54,370
to offer your method of reversing aging

616
00:29:54,400 --> 00:29:55,920
and maintaining eternal youth

617
00:29:56,250 --> 00:29:57,320
to the old City Lord.

618
00:29:57,450 --> 00:30:00,130
This way, we can safeguard our human race's future.

619
00:30:08,750 --> 00:30:10,710
Tanyin, here you are.

620
00:30:11,570 --> 00:30:12,570
Have you eaten?

621
00:30:12,570 --> 00:30:13,330
Are you hungry?

622
00:30:13,770 --> 00:30:14,920
We brought some snacks back.

623
00:30:14,920 --> 00:30:15,920
Try one quickly.

624
00:30:16,490 --> 00:30:17,610
You're so kind.

625
00:30:17,810 --> 00:30:18,960
She has gotten on

626
00:30:18,960 --> 00:30:20,280
Madam Zhi Dai's good side.

627
00:30:20,280 --> 00:30:21,160
Instead of practicing,

628
00:30:21,160 --> 00:30:22,280
she can hide here and slack off.

629
00:30:22,280 --> 00:30:23,160
How could she be hungry?

630
00:30:24,680 --> 00:30:25,480
Quick, have a taste.

631
00:30:29,490 --> 00:30:30,370
Is it good?

632
00:30:31,640 --> 00:30:32,810
I made these.

633
00:30:32,960 --> 00:30:33,890
We were in the kitchen this afternoon,

634
00:30:33,890 --> 00:30:34,950
practicing our culinary skills.

635
00:30:35,040 --> 00:30:36,850
The ingredients in the kitchen are all excellent.

636
00:30:36,850 --> 00:30:37,800
So the taste of what we make

637
00:30:37,800 --> 00:30:38,970
naturally can't be bad.

638
00:30:39,240 --> 00:30:40,200
Have some more.

639
00:30:40,530 --> 00:30:41,310
Thank you.

640
00:30:43,490 --> 00:30:44,490
Do you know?

641
00:30:44,690 --> 00:30:46,600
Today is the White Robe Festival of the Youhu Clan.

642
00:30:46,890 --> 00:30:47,850
White Robe Festival?

643
00:30:47,970 --> 00:30:48,970
What kind of festival is that?

644
00:30:49,560 --> 00:30:51,830
It's when the Youhu Clan pays tribute to ghosts and gods

645
00:30:51,870 --> 00:30:53,360
and worships their ancestors.

646
00:30:53,440 --> 00:30:54,960
The Youhu Clan are already divine beings themselves.

647
00:30:54,960 --> 00:30:56,130
Do they still need to worship ghosts and gods?

648
00:30:56,450 --> 00:30:58,410
How can they be considered divine beings?

649
00:30:58,440 --> 00:31:00,360
The Youhu Clan is just like us humans.

650
00:31:00,410 --> 00:31:01,800
We're all mortal beings.

651
00:31:03,810 --> 00:31:04,690
Tell me,

652
00:31:04,720 --> 00:31:07,250
are there really ghosts and monsters in this world?

653
00:31:07,250 --> 00:31:08,160
Of course there are.

654
00:31:08,160 --> 00:31:09,280
I've even seen one.

655
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:10,600
I was still young at that time.

656
00:31:10,600 --> 00:31:11,480
I remember one year,

657
00:31:11,480 --> 00:31:12,360
during the Zhongyuan Festival,

658
00:31:12,360 --> 00:31:13,640
my parents took me out.

659
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:14,970
We accidentally got separated.

660
00:31:15,370 --> 00:31:16,880
I was crying and searching.

661
00:31:17,080 --> 00:31:18,690
Somehow I ended up by the lake.

662
00:31:19,010 --> 00:31:20,280
I squatted by the lake and called out,

663
00:31:20,480 --> 00:31:21,850
"Father, Mother!"

664
00:31:22,290 --> 00:31:24,000
Suddenly I heard my mother respond.

665
00:31:24,290 --> 00:31:25,880
I looked towards the sound.

666
00:31:26,440 --> 00:31:28,370
There was a big mass of hair in the lake

667
00:31:28,810 --> 00:31:30,400
and a pale white face.

668
00:31:31,080 --> 00:31:31,840
That face looked like

669
00:31:31,840 --> 00:31:33,530
it had been sewn with a sewing needle.

670
00:31:34,010 --> 00:31:35,440
It was full of cracks.

671
00:31:36,060 --> 00:31:36,850
And just like that,

672
00:31:37,240 --> 00:31:38,490
it was waving at me

673
00:31:38,810 --> 00:31:40,050
and calling my name.

674
00:31:40,760 --> 00:31:41,690
Then what?

675
00:31:42,210 --> 00:31:43,530
Then I ran away, of course!

676
00:31:43,530 --> 00:31:44,160
Later, I heard

677
00:31:44,160 --> 00:31:45,330
from an elderly neighbor

678
00:31:45,330 --> 00:31:47,000
that I had encountered a tailor ghost.

679
00:31:47,170 --> 00:31:48,080
A tailor ghost?

680
00:31:48,490 --> 00:31:50,170
It's a type of water ghost.

681
00:31:50,570 --> 00:31:51,490
They accidentally

682
00:31:51,490 --> 00:31:52,450
drowned in the water

683
00:31:52,480 --> 00:31:54,010
and their bodies were eaten by fish and shrimp.

684
00:31:54,210 --> 00:31:55,280
With no remains,

685
00:31:55,560 --> 00:31:56,770
they cannot reincarnate.

686
00:31:57,120 --> 00:31:58,290
To find release,

687
00:31:58,320 --> 00:31:59,680
they lure passersby into the water

688
00:31:59,930 --> 00:32:00,760
to take

689
00:32:00,760 --> 00:32:02,320
organs similar to their own

690
00:32:02,440 --> 00:32:04,160
and sew a new body.

691
00:32:10,050 --> 00:32:11,450
Stop talking about this.

692
00:32:11,810 --> 00:32:13,440
You're scaring Tanyin.

693
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:14,280
I'm not afraid.

694
00:32:16,890 --> 00:32:18,160
Madam Zhi Dai is asking someone

695
00:32:18,160 --> 00:32:20,040
to bring tea and snacks to Steward Sheng Xiang.

696
00:32:20,040 --> 00:32:21,170
Who wants to go?

697
00:32:24,610 --> 00:32:25,640
No one? Fine.

698
00:32:25,640 --> 00:32:26,840
Then I'll go myself.

699
00:32:28,400 --> 00:32:29,210
That tailor ghost...

700
00:32:29,210 --> 00:32:29,970
Wait a moment.

701
00:32:31,290 --> 00:32:32,090
I'll go.

702
00:32:32,800 --> 00:32:34,530
Today is the White Robe Festival of the Youhu Clan.

703
00:32:34,640 --> 00:32:35,560
It's similar to our human's

704
00:32:35,560 --> 00:32:36,570
Ghost Festival.

705
00:32:36,570 --> 00:32:38,330
But I saw a large mass of hair in the water.

706
00:32:38,330 --> 00:32:40,040
There was a pale face within the hair,

707
00:32:40,040 --> 00:32:41,160
covered in cracks,

708
00:32:41,160 --> 00:32:41,970
as if it had been

709
00:32:41,970 --> 00:32:43,000
sewn together with a needle.

710
00:32:55,650 --> 00:32:56,450
Oh, it's you.

711
00:33:00,520 --> 00:33:01,330
I

712
00:33:02,040 --> 00:33:03,600
didn't plan to see you today.

713
00:33:03,920 --> 00:33:04,720
What a coincidence.

714
00:33:05,030 --> 00:33:06,630
I didn't come to see you on purpose either.

715
00:33:22,050 --> 00:33:23,570
Aren't you human maids

716
00:33:23,570 --> 00:33:25,040
supposed to be living on Xiaoxiang Peak?

717
00:33:25,280 --> 00:33:26,330
Why are you following me?

718
00:33:27,040 --> 00:33:27,920
It's along the way.

719
00:33:28,450 --> 00:33:29,530
You say that, but do you know

720
00:33:29,530 --> 00:33:30,360
where I'm going?

721
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:32,200
It's in the same direction anyway.

722
00:34:05,550 --> 00:34:06,930
Are you afraid of walking at night?

723
00:34:09,159 --> 00:34:10,159
Of course not.

724
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:11,360
Then you're afraid of ghosts?

725
00:34:12,239 --> 00:34:14,000
There are no ghosts in this world.

726
00:34:15,679 --> 00:34:16,760
If there are gods in this world,

727
00:34:17,250 --> 00:34:18,489
how can there be no ghosts?

728
00:34:19,320 --> 00:34:21,120
That's because after the war between gods and demons,

729
00:34:21,250 --> 00:34:22,239
Deity Taihe

730
00:34:22,270 --> 00:34:23,750
suppressed the demon clan with primordial power.

731
00:34:23,850 --> 00:34:24,920
The Demon Lord is dead.

732
00:34:25,000 --> 00:34:26,290
All evil and darkness in this world

733
00:34:26,290 --> 00:34:27,370
have been dispersed.

734
00:34:30,000 --> 00:34:31,250
What day is it today?

735
00:34:34,449 --> 00:34:35,280
The White Robe Festival.

736
00:34:38,199 --> 00:34:40,730
We of the Youhu Clan have no cemeteries.

737
00:34:40,929 --> 00:34:42,960
After death, we are refined into ashes

738
00:34:43,370 --> 00:34:44,570
and scattered under peach trees,

739
00:34:44,840 --> 00:34:45,889
becoming spring soil

740
00:34:46,159 --> 00:34:47,239
to nourish the peach wood.

741
00:34:47,530 --> 00:34:48,560
So we believe

742
00:34:48,560 --> 00:34:49,800
that every peach blossom

743
00:34:50,150 --> 00:34:51,949
is another continuation of life.

744
00:34:53,320 --> 00:34:54,480
Every peach blossom

745
00:34:55,250 --> 00:34:57,130
is also our blood relative.

746
00:35:01,760 --> 00:35:03,080
I came to pay respects to my ancestors.

747
00:35:03,560 --> 00:35:04,640
What are you here for?

748
00:35:09,330 --> 00:35:10,360
And you say you're not afraid.

749
00:35:11,610 --> 00:35:12,440
You don't understand.

750
00:35:12,850 --> 00:35:14,000
I'm not afraid,

751
00:35:15,570 --> 00:35:17,340
I just don't like this atmosphere.

752
00:35:20,490 --> 00:35:21,490
Still not afraid?

753
00:35:43,470 --> 00:35:45,070
What are you looking for?

754
00:35:45,090 --> 00:35:46,380
Search thoroughly for me.

755
00:35:46,410 --> 00:35:47,070
Yes.

756
00:36:00,200 --> 00:36:01,280
The patrol discovered

757
00:36:01,400 --> 00:36:03,600
someone performing curse rituals on the back mountain.

758
00:36:03,690 --> 00:36:04,390
They were said to be wearing

759
00:36:04,390 --> 00:36:06,240
the attire of our Xiaoxiang Peak maids.

760
00:36:06,650 --> 00:36:08,480
Today, we'll take a good look

761
00:36:08,730 --> 00:36:10,850
at who harbors evil intentions

762
00:36:11,000 --> 00:36:12,200
and seeks their own demise.

763
00:36:12,540 --> 00:36:13,340
Search carefully.

764
00:36:13,370 --> 00:36:14,020
Yes.

765
00:36:47,530 --> 00:36:49,450
Madam, we haven't found anything.

766
00:37:13,240 --> 00:37:14,040
Tanyin.

767
00:37:16,040 --> 00:37:17,850
Tanyin, are you asleep?

768
00:37:18,240 --> 00:37:19,600
I have something to ask you.

769
00:37:39,360 --> 00:37:40,730
Tanyin, did you take

770
00:37:40,730 --> 00:37:42,170
my things?

771
00:37:42,760 --> 00:37:43,800
What things?

772
00:37:44,320 --> 00:37:45,600
My luggage.

773
00:37:46,160 --> 00:37:47,160
I didn't take it.

774
00:37:47,240 --> 00:37:47,970
Is there anything

775
00:37:47,970 --> 00:37:49,450
important in your luggage?

776
00:37:49,770 --> 00:37:50,560
If there is,

777
00:37:50,560 --> 00:37:52,050
you can report to the instructor

778
00:37:52,270 --> 00:37:53,520
and ask her to help you find it.

779
00:38:01,810 --> 00:38:04,080
[Liujiao Palace]

780
00:38:05,910 --> 00:38:06,830
General Chiyi!

781
00:38:18,390 --> 00:38:19,180
Catch him!

782
00:38:19,220 --> 00:38:19,940
Commander...

783
00:38:20,210 --> 00:38:21,280
General Chiyi was poisoned.

784
00:38:21,310 --> 00:38:22,150
Go report this immediately!

785
00:38:22,190 --> 00:38:22,920
Anyone who runs into him

786
00:38:22,920 --> 00:38:23,800
should first protect themselves.

787
00:38:23,800 --> 00:38:25,250
Then try to capture him if possible!

788
00:38:25,290 --> 00:38:25,940
Understood!

789
00:38:28,550 --> 00:38:29,360
What's wrong?

790
00:38:30,410 --> 00:38:31,340
Something happened.

791
00:38:42,000 --> 00:38:42,800
Chiyi?

792
00:38:43,250 --> 00:38:44,330
He's not Chiyi!

793
00:38:44,590 --> 00:38:45,660
What do you mean

794
00:38:45,690 --> 00:38:46,450
he's not Chiyi?

795
00:38:46,530 --> 00:38:47,800
He wreaked havoc in the Jinxia Palace

796
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:49,040
and injured many of our people

797
00:38:49,120 --> 00:38:50,400
as if he were controlled by someone.

798
00:38:54,370 --> 00:38:55,280
Hey, bastard,

799
00:38:55,970 --> 00:38:57,690
we meet again.

800
00:38:58,640 --> 00:38:59,960
What tricks are you playing?

801
00:39:00,350 --> 00:39:01,200
Too bad

802
00:39:01,660 --> 00:39:03,150
that I missed my strike.

803
00:39:04,600 --> 00:39:05,480
So

804
00:39:06,290 --> 00:39:08,090
I still can't kill you today.

805
00:39:09,290 --> 00:39:11,010
I'm here to annihilate you,

806
00:39:11,680 --> 00:39:13,520
every last one of you!

807
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:19,480
Just you wait.

808
00:39:19,970 --> 00:39:22,440
This is just the beginning.

809
00:39:36,080 --> 00:39:36,990
Yuanzhong,

810
00:39:38,040 --> 00:39:40,630
we'll be back!

811
00:39:43,690 --> 00:39:44,560
Chiyi!

812
00:39:45,410 --> 00:39:46,570
Could this be the War Demons'

813
00:39:46,610 --> 00:39:47,580
possessing technique?

814
00:39:48,020 --> 00:39:49,780
Go to Tianqu Peak and find Elder Dingxu now!

815
00:39:49,810 --> 00:39:50,450
-Got it. -Got it.
